# Thesis Dashboard Implementation

## Goal

Build a **time-step pipeline dashboard** for the masters thesis: "Adaptive skill and stake in forecast markets". The dashboard must show a coherent, step-by-step flow: **Inputs ‚Üí DGP ‚Üí Core (with sub-components) ‚Üí Behaviour ‚Üí Results**, plus **Experiments** in separate tabs.

## Reference

- Plan: `dashboard/docs/THESIS_DASHBOARD_PLAN.md`
